uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.filter

Class OptionalFilterConverter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.jdbc.filter.OptionalFilterConverter<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FilterVisitor<BaseFilter<T>,T>

    public class OptionalFilterConverter<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FilterVisitor<BaseFilter<T>,T>
    Helper classes to convert generic filters into SQLFilters. Unlike FilterConverter this returns the original filter if conversion is not possible
